      "id": "footer_note",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1895,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 18,
      "text": "All connectors share: CachedMCPClient (SSE transport)  |  ConnectorMetrics (Prometheus)  |  Health server (/health + /metrics)  |  Heartbeat task  |  FilteredEventBuffer  |  Checkpoint-after-acceptance semantics",
      "originalText": "All connectors share: CachedMCPClient (SSE transport)  |  ConnectorMetrics (Prometheus)  |  Health server (/health + /metrics)  |  Heartbeat task  |  FilteredEventBuffer  |  Checkpoint-after-acceptance semantics",
