    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "infra_blobstore_txt",
      "x": 356,
      "y": 1991,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 258,
      "text": "BlobStore (S3-compatible)\n\nAttachment storage\n\nFetch modes:\n  eager — at ingest time\n  lazy  — ref written, fetch\n          on-demand\n\nPer-MIME size limits:\n  image/*  → 5 MB\n  PDF      → 15 MB\n  Sheets   → 10 MB\n  Documents→ 10 MB\n\nSkipped if oversized\n(metrics: attachment_skipped_oversized)",
      "originalText": "BlobStore (S3-compatible)\n\nAttachment storage\n\nFetch modes:\n  eager — at ingest time\n  lazy  — ref written, fetch\n          on-demand\n\nPer-MIME size limits:\n  image/*  → 5 MB\n  PDF      → 15 MB\n  Sheets   → 10 MB\n  Documents→ 10 MB\n\nSkipped if oversized\n(metrics: attachment_skipped_oversized)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1f2937",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
