    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "infra_pubsub_txt",
      "x": 626,
      "y": 1991,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 258,
      "text": "GCP Pub/Sub (Gmail Push)\n\nGmail push notification path\n\nAPI: users.watch()\nRenewal: every 24h\n  (GMAIL_WATCH_RENEW_INTERVAL_S)\n\nPub/Sub topic:\n  GMAIL_PUBSUB_TOPIC\n\nWebhook receiver:\n  FastAPI on port 40083\n  path: /gmail/webhook\n  auth token: GMAIL_PUBSUB_WEBHOOK_TOKEN\n\nFallback: bounded polling\nif push unavailable",
      "originalText": "GCP Pub/Sub (Gmail Push)\n\nGmail push notification path\n\nAPI: users.watch()\nRenewal: every 24h\n  (GMAIL_WATCH_RENEW_INTERVAL_S)\n\nPub/Sub topic:\n  GMAIL_PUBSUB_TOPIC\n\nWebhook receiver:\n  FastAPI on port 40083\n  path: /gmail/webhook\n  auth token: GMAIL_PUBSUB_WEBHOOK_TOKEN\n\nFallback: bounded polling\nif push unavailable",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1f2937",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
