    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "infra_health_txt",
      "x": 896,
      "y": 1991,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 258,
      "text": "Health Server (FastAPI/uvicorn)\n\nShared: health_socket.py\n  SO_REUSEADDR pre-bind\n  SIGTERM stale port holder\n\nEndpoints:\n  GET /health → HealthStatus\n  GET /metrics → Prometheus\n\nPorts:\n  40081 — Telegram Bot\n  40082 — Gmail\n  40083 — Gmail Pub/Sub webhook\n  40084 — Discord\n\nK8s readiness + liveness probes",
      "originalText": "Health Server (FastAPI/uvicorn)\n\nShared: health_socket.py\n  SO_REUSEADDR pre-bind\n  SIGTERM stale port holder\n\nEndpoints:\n  GET /health → HealthStatus\n  GET /metrics → Prometheus\n\nPorts:\n  40081 — Telegram Bot\n  40082 — Gmail\n  40083 — Gmail Pub/Sub webhook\n  40084 — Discord\n\nK8s readiness + liveness probes",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1f2937",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
