    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "infra_credstore_txt",
      "x": 1166,
      "y": 1991,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 258,
      "text": "CredentialStore\n\nResolution order:\n  1. DB (shared.contact_info,\n     secured=true)\n  2. Environment variable\n\nCredential types:\n  Gmail: OAuth tokens\n  Telegram Bot: bot token\n  Telegram User: session +\n    API ID + API hash\n  Discord: bot token\n\nNever committed to source.\nRotate on exposure.",
      "originalText": "CredentialStore\n\nResolution order:\n  1. DB (shared.contact_info,\n     secured=true)\n  2. Environment variable\n\nCredential types:\n  Gmail: OAuth tokens\n  Telegram Bot: bot token\n  Telegram User: session +\n    API ID + API hash\n  Discord: bot token\n\nNever committed to source.\nRotate on exposure.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
