    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "policy_layer1_txt",
      "x": 86,
      "y": 2399,
      "width": 378,
      "height": 338,
      "text": "Layer 1: Label Include/Exclude Filter\n(LabelFilterPolicy — spec §9)\n\nRuns FIRST — gates ingestion before tiering\n\nExclude check (precedence over include):\n  message label in GMAIL_LABEL_EXCLUDE\n  → should_ingest=False\n  → filter_reason: label_exclude:<LABEL>\n\nInclude check:\n  GMAIL_LABEL_INCLUDE empty → allow all\n  message label not in GMAIL_LABEL_INCLUDE\n  → should_ingest=False\n  → filter_reason: label_not_in_include_list\n\nDefault policy:\n  exclude: [SPAM, TRASH]\n  include: [] (allow all others)\n\nOutput:\n  (should_ingest: bool, filter_reason: str)\n\nMetric: butlers_connector_gmail_label_filter_total\n  labels: [filter_action, reason]",
      "originalText": "Layer 1: Label Include/Exclude Filter\n(LabelFilterPolicy — spec §9)\n\nRuns FIRST — gates ingestion before tiering\n\nExclude check (precedence over include):\n  message label in GMAIL_LABEL_EXCLUDE\n  → should_ingest=False\n  → filter_reason: label_exclude:<LABEL>\n\nInclude check:\n  GMAIL_LABEL_INCLUDE empty → allow all\n  message label not in GMAIL_LABEL_INCLUDE\n  → should_ingest=False\n  → filter_reason: label_not_in_include_list\n\nDefault policy:\n  exclude: [SPAM, TRASH]\n  include: [] (allow all others)\n\nOutput:\n  (should_ingest: bool, filter_reason: str)\n\nMetric: butlers_connector_gmail_label_filter_total\n  labels: [filter_action, reason]",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 201003,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 201004,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": null,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": "policy_layer1",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "policy_layer2",
      "x": 510,
      "y": 2393,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 350,
      "strokeColor": "#1d4ed8",
      "backgroundColor": "#eff6ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 202001,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 202002,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "policy_layer2_txt",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "policy_layer2_txt",
      "x": 516,
      "y": 2399,
      "width": 408,
      "height": 338,
      "text": "Layer 2: Policy Tier Assignment\n(PolicyTierAssigner — spec §2.2)\n\nRuns AFTER label filter passes\nFirst rule match wins\n\nRule 1 → high_priority\n  sender in known_contacts\n  rule: known_contact\n\nRule 2 → high_priority\n  In-Reply-To header references a\n  user-sent message id\n  rule: reply_to_outbound\n\nRule 3 → interactive\n  user email in To/Cc header\n  AND no List-Unsubscribe\n  AND no bulk Precedence header\n  rule: direct_correspondence\n\nRule 4 → default (fallback)\n  rule: fallback_default\n\nOutput: (policy_tier, assignment_rule)\nWrites to envelope control.policy_tier\n\nMetric: butlers_connector_gmail_priority_tier_assigned_total",
      "originalText": "Layer 2: Policy Tier Assignment\n(PolicyTierAssigner — spec §2.2)\n\nRuns AFTER label filter passes\nFirst rule match wins\n\nRule 1 → high_priority\n  sender in known_contacts\n  rule: known_contact\n\nRule 2 → high_priority\n  In-Reply-To header references a\n  user-sent message id\n  rule: reply_to_outbound\n\nRule 3 → interactive\n  user email in To/Cc header\n  AND no List-Unsubscribe\n  AND no bulk Precedence header\n  rule: direct_correspondence\n\nRule 4 → default (fallback)\n  rule: fallback_default\n\nOutput: (policy_tier, assignment_rule)\nWrites to envelope control.policy_tier\n\nMetric: butlers_connector_gmail_priority_tier_assigned_total",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 202003,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 202004,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
