      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "policy_layer3_txt",
      "x": 976,
      "y": 2399,
      "width": 428,
      "height": 338,
      "text": "Layer 3: Ingestion Tier Classification\n(classify_ingestion_tier — spec §4)\n\nMaps triage_action → ingestion_tier:\n\n  route_to:*         → Tier 1 (full)\n  low_priority_queue → Tier 1 (full, deferred)\n  pass_through       → Tier 1 (safety default)\n  metadata_only      → Tier 2 (metadata-only)\n  skip               → Tier 3 (skip)\n\nTier 1: full pipeline\n  route + classify + process + store\n  ingestion_tier name: \"full\"\n\nTier 2: metadata-only pipeline\n  store reference, no LLM classification\n  ingestion_tier name: \"metadata\"\n\nTier 3: skip pipeline\n  do not submit to Switchboard\n  ingestion_tier name: \"skip\"\n\nCurrent Gmail: always pass_through → Tier 1\nFuture: ingestion_rules table drives tier\n\nMetric: butlers_connector_gmail_tier_assigned_total",
      "originalText": "Layer 3: Ingestion Tier Classification\n(classify_ingestion_tier — spec §4)\n\nMaps triage_action → ingestion_tier:\n\n  route_to:*         → Tier 1 (full)\n  low_priority_queue → Tier 1 (full, deferred)\n  pass_through       → Tier 1 (safety default)\n  metadata_only      → Tier 2 (metadata-only)\n  skip               → Tier 3 (skip)\n\nTier 1: full pipeline\n  route + classify + process + store\n  ingestion_tier name: \"full\"\n\nTier 2: metadata-only pipeline\n  store reference, no LLM classification\n  ingestion_tier name: \"metadata\"\n\nTier 3: skip pipeline\n  do not submit to Switchboard\n  ingestion_tier name: \"skip\"\n\nCurrent Gmail: always pass_through → Tier 1\nFuture: ingestion_rules table drives tier\n\nMetric: butlers_connector_gmail_tier_assigned_total",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
